INSERT INTO integration_connection
                  (
                    id,
                    user_id,
                    connection_id,
                    provider_kind,
                    status,
                    failure_message,
                    notifications_sync_failures,
                    tasks_sync_failures,
                    first_notifications_sync_failed_at,
                    first_tasks_sync_failed_at,
                    created_at,
                    updated_at
                  )
                VALUES
                  (
                    $1,
                    $2,
                    $3,
                    $4::integration_provider_kind,
                    $5::integration_connection_status,
                    $6,
                    $7,
                    $8,
                    $9,
                    $10,
                    $11,
                    $12
                  )
